Package cellularland1

  • Class Summary 
    Class Description
    AutomatonGenerator
    Static class that provides generating new random automata with the parameters specified.
    ButtonNode
    Wrap around a button, used to easily distinguish the state of the button.
    CAutomaton
    Encapsulates a cellular automaton, mainly its transition function and the initial position.
    CellularLand1
    Entry point of the application.
    FXMLDocumentController
    FXML controller of the XML document, contains the objects injected by FXML and all the listeners to events by usage of active controls in GUI.
    GridController
    The controller of the grid with the main board.
    Loader
    Loads the cellular automaton from specified text file, parser.
    ManaController
    Controller of the mana bar.
    Mechanics
    The singleton class the contains the main mechanics, interface between the graphics and the automaton.
    NapovedaText
    This is just a static class to contain all the text of help - so that I don't have to put it in a place where it would clutter the code.
    StatisticsRecord
    The encapsulation of a record in statistics database.
